# HubSpot Certificate Webhook URLs
# Each course and graduation has its own HubSpot webhook trigger URL.
# Format: https://api-na1.hubapi.com/automation/v4/webhook-triggers/<portalId>/<triggerId>

# --- Entrepreneur Academy (legacy single-webhook setup) ---
# ENTREPRENEUR_ACADEMY_HUBSPOT_WEBHOOK=
# CODEBASE_CERTIFICATE_HUBSPOT_WEBHOOK=

